text: Marie-Hélène Syre (born 5 March 1958) is a French equestrian. She competed in two events at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1958 births Category:Living people Category:French female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of France Category:Equestrians at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Rouen
